videos.title: 2020 Spring Valley 100 - Gravel Cycling
videos.description: The 2020 Spring Valley 100 Gravel Bike Race was cancelled so we hit the course on the planned date anyways.  The course is similar to the Almanzo of the past.

videos.title: Almanzo 100 - 2017 - Spring Valley, Minnesota - The Wet Edition
videos.description:
May 20, 2017 marked the 11th running of Almanzo 100, often considered the Granddaddy of all gravel races. This edition will be remembered as the wettest in the history of the race. 1.47" of rain fell in the Twin Cities on that day, just two hours further north.

videos.title: Staging & Roll-Out for the Royal Gravel Road Race
videos.description:
Watch the staging and starting roll-out of the Royal Gravel Road Race.
The Royal is a 162 miles of gloriously hilly gravel riding. The race departs from Spring Valley, Minnesota a couple of hours before the Almanzo 100 Gravel Race.
A truly Royal event
May 18, 2013
